---
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout>
  <section class="my-4 max-w-[300px] lg:max-w-6xl text-left mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center my-4">About Us</h2>
    <p>
      We are a web development company committed to delivering high-quality and
      reliable web solutions to businesses of all sizes. Our team of experienced
      web developers, designers, and project managers work together to create
      custom, user-friendly websites that are tailored to our clients' unique
      needs. At our company, we believe in the power of technology to transform
      businesses and drive growth. Whether you need a simple landing page or a
      complex full-stack application, we have the expertise to deliver results
      that exceed your expectations.
    </p>
    <br>
    <br>
    <p>
      We pride ourselves on our ability to create custom solutions that are
      scalable, flexible, and designed to meet your specific goals. We
      specialize in a range of web development technologies, including the
      latest front-end frameworks like React and Angular, as well as back-end
      technologies like Node.js and Laravel. We also have extensive experience
      developing WordPress websites, and can provide custom themes and plugins
      to enhance your site's functionality. At our company, we believe in
      transparency and open communication. We work closely with our clients to
      ensure that they are involved in every step of the development process,
      from planning and design to deployment and maintenance. Our goal is to
      provide you with a website that not only looks great, but is also fast,
      secure, and user-friendly. Thank you for considering our web development
      company for your next project. We look forward to working with you and
      helping your business succeed online!
    </p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
